Nadiya Bychkova, 32, confirmed she was in a relationship with Strictly Come Dancing co-star Kai Widdrington, 26, in April, after rumours began swirling in January during the show's tour. The star gushed over her new man as she watched his latest dance show. She shared the pictures of Kai planting a kiss on her cheek in view of her 138,000 Instagram followers. Nadiya captioned the picture: "What an opening night! "The proudest girlfriend @kaiwidd." After being pictured looking cosy together, Nadiya confirmed the news of their relationship in April, revealing she and Kai had been dating "for a couple of months now".